5:
Hao was begging to visit Palpebra
all morning, but now we're actually
here, he's just, uh...
12:
I'm studying the huma—
I mean, uh... J-just looking around.
16:
Great... Now, why are you "studying"
people?
22: That's why I need to be...
28:
THAT'S what you've been moping
around all week for?
31:
I was thinking about what to do, and
then it hit me—
33: I want to be like Alk.
38: NO! You don't have to... to...
42:
Hey! You're the boy I met the other
day, right?
45:
I figured you were an adventurer, so
I wasn't sure I'd be able to find you
again. I'm so glad I did!
48: Is this the girl Hao saved?
52: It is. I remember her scent.
55:
You remember me? O-oh, wow, I
uh... Heh...
61:
Of course not! I'm Lisa, by the way.
I've been looking all over so I could
apologize to you!
62:
I'm REALLY sorry my mom was so
rude to you. I didn't even get to
thank you, so... Thanks for saving me.
66:
*sigh* Mom's been suuuper strict
since the kidnapping thing. She
won't let me leave the house at all!
69:
Wait, but then why are you—
Did you sneak out?
73: Not bad. You've got guts, kid.
76:
Well, I had no choice!
"Hao," right? I... I really want to be
your friend! Is that okay?
79: You don't need to ask us, Hao.
83: Do what YOU feel is right.
88: Lisa. I, I would like to be your friend.
91:
REALLY?! Then let's go on a date! A
date!
97:
You'll see! I'll take you around the
best date spots in Palpebra!
100:
Have fun! Just... he better be home
by dinner, got it?
104: Oh, c'mon. You sound like Light.
112: I-I'm not THAT fussy... am I?
118:
Hao! Haooo!
...He has to be around somewhere.
122: Oh, I'm pretty sure he's out with Lisa.
126:
Again?! What time do they think it
is? Did he say where they were
going?
129:
No, but they've gotta be in Palpebra
somewhere... probably?
136: What in the blazes was that?!
144:
I feel kinda dizzy... haha.
But that was AMAZING!
149:
This is the place you were telling me
about, right? Your favorite part of
the forest?
151:
Yes. I have a lot of memories with
friends here. It's also where I met Alk
and the others.
153: You remind me a lot of him.
156: Who, Alk? But I'm your girlfri—
157:
Oh, never mind. He IS pretty cute, so
I'll take that as a compliment.
...Y-you're way hotter than Alk
though!
159:
Hotter? I haven't learned that word
yet, but if Alk is cute and "hotter," so
are you.
162: I'll do my best to be "hotter" too.
